<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- lanā fī kalạmi ạlại̹lahi ạlṣãmad̊
 ạảsāsuⁿ lại̹ymāninā kāl̊jabal̊
 wahal̊ min̊ mazīdiⁿ ʿalay̱ mā waʿad̊
 liman̊ jāʾahu waʿalaẙhi ạtãkal̊

[V2]
 2- yaqūlu ạṭ̊mayỉnã fāi̹nĩy maʿak̊
 wāi̹nĩy ại̹lahuka wāl̊ʿaẘnu bī
 wāi̹nĩy ạủqawĩyka kaẙ ạảr̊faʿak̊
 wāảr̊tẖī liḍaʿ̊fika mitẖ̊la ạlạảbi

[V3]
 3- ại̹dẖā kẖuḍ̊ta lujã ạl̊mīāhi ạl̊ʿamīq̊
 falạ taq̊diranã ʿalaẙka ạllũjaj̊
 ạảnā laka fī ạlḍĩyqi niʿ̊ma ạlrãfīq̊
 waḍīquka ạủb̊diluhu biạl̊faraj̊

[V4]
 4- ại̹dẖā mā dahāka balạʾu ạl̊kẖaṭar̊
 fayak̊fīka min̊ niʿ̊matī mā ạn̊sakab̊
 walạ tūqiʿu ạlnãạru fīka ạlḍãrar̊
 fāi̹nĩy ạủnaqĩyka mitẖ̊la ạldẖãhab̊

[V5]
 5- waḥubĩy sayab̊qay̱ sẖadīda ạlrũsūkẖ̊
 wayad̊rīhi sẖaʿ̊bī biṭūli ạlzãmān̊
 ại̹dẖā kalãla ạlsẖãẙbu rā̊̉sa ạlsẖũywukẖ̊
 biluṭ̊fiⁿ ạảqūduhumu biạl̊ḥanān̊

[V6]
 6- famā nāla kaẙdu ạl̊ʿadūĩ ạl̊kẖaṣīm̊
 walạ kẖāba man̊ līasūʿa ạs̊tanad̊
 wāi̹n̊ hāja ḍidãhu jun̊du ạl̊jaḥīm̊
 falas̊tu bitārikihi lilạảbad̊</lyrics>
<aka>lnạ fy klạm ạlạ̹lh ạlṣmd</aka>
<title>nry̱ fy klạm ạlạ̹lh ạlṣmd</title>
<author>jwn kyn , nạṣyf ạlyạzjy, John Francis Wade</author>
<hymn_number>1316</hymn_number>
</song>